/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"s_tab fade \" id=\"tabtabthree\">\r\n                            <div class=\"tab_content one\"  style=\"background-image:url(https:\/\/waterfrontsmiles.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/15.png)\" >\r\n                                <div class=\"content_image\">\r\n                                                                                                              <h2 class=\"tabtitle\">Smarter Dentistry for Better Results<\/h2>\r\n                                                                                                                <p>We use state-of-the-art technology, including digital X-rays, laser dentistry, and minimally invasive techniques, to make treatments faster, safer, and more comfortable. Our advanced equipment helps us diagnose accurately, plan precisely, and deliver superior outcomes that protect and enhance your smile\u2019s long-term health.<\/p>\r\n                                                                                                                <a href=\"https:\/\/waterfrontsmiles.com\/about-us\/\"  target=&quot;_blank&quot;  rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; class=\"rd_more\">\r\n                                            Read More                                            <i class=\"icon-right-arrow\"><\/i>\r\n                                        <\/a>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"s_tab fade \" id=\"tabtabtfour\">\r\n                            <div class=\"tab_content one\"  style=\"background-image:url(https:\/\/waterfrontsmiles.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/10.png)\" >\r\n                                <div class=\"content_image\">\r\n                                                                                                              <h2 class=\"tabtitle\">Quality Dentistry at Affordable<\/h2>\r\n                                                                                                                <p>We believe everyone deserves access to excellent dental care. That\u2019s why we accept most insurance plans and offer our own \u201cWaterfront Family Loyalty Program\u201d for uninsured patients. It\u2019s an affordable, worry-free way to receive regular checkups, cleanings, and discounted treatments all year long.<\/p>\r\n                                                                                                                <a href=\"https:\/\/waterfrontsmiles.com\/about-us\/\"  target=&quot;_blank&quot;  rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; class=\"rd_more\">\r\n                                            Read More                                            <i class=\"icon-right-arrow\"><\/i>\r\n                                        <\/a>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"s_tab fade \" id=\"tabtabfive\">\r\n                            <div class=\"tab_content one\"  style=\"background-image:url(https:\/\/waterfrontsmiles.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/13.png)\" >\r\n                                <div class=\"content_image\">\r\n                                                                                                              <h2 class=\"tabtitle\">Building Smiles<\/h2>\r\n                                                                                                                <p>We\u2019re more than just a dental office, we\u2019re part of the Frisco community. From supporting local families to treating patients of all ages, we take pride in caring for our neighbors. Our family-oriented approach ensures every visit feels personal, friendly, and genuinely welcoming.<\/p>\r\n                                                                                                                <a href=\"https:\/\/waterfrontsmiles.com\/about-us\/\"  target=&quot;_blank&quot;  rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; class=\"rd_more\">\r\n                                            Contact us                                            <i class=\"icon-right-arrow\"><\/i>\r\n                                        <\/a>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <!-- default style end -->\r\n        \r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/section>\r\n\r\n \t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ef4594a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ef4594a\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;shape_divider_bottom&quot;:&quot;waves-pattern&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shape elementor-shape-bottom\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-negative=\"false\">\n\t\t\t<svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1047.1 3.7\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMin slice\">\n\t<path class=\"elementor-shape-fill\" d=\"M1047.1,0C557,0,8.9,0,0,0v1.6c0,0,0.6-1.5,2.7-0.3C3.9,2,6.1,4.1,8.3,3.5c0.9-0.2,1.5-1.9,1.5-1.9\ts0.6-1.5,2.7-0.3C13.8,2,16,4.1,18.2,3.5c0.9-0.2,1.5-1.9,1.5-1.9s0.6-1.5,2.7-0.3C23.6,2,25.9,4.1,28,3.5c0.9-0.2,1.5-1.9,1.5-1.9\tc0,0,0.6-1.5,2.7-0.3c1.2,0.7,3.5,2.8,5.6,2.2c0.9-0.2,1.5-1.9,1.5-1.9c0,0,0.6-1.5,2.7-0.3c1.2,0.7,3.5,2.8,5.6,2.2\tc0.9-0.2,1.5-1.9,1.5-1.9s0.